          body {
          cursor: url('images/cursor-image.png'), auto;
          }
          
          a:hover{
          cursor: url('images/ cursor-image-hover.png'), auto!important;
          }


OR:

To make the click/hover point in the centre of the custom cursor (rather than top left corner), upload the png to:
https://www.cursor.cc/

After downloading the file and uploading it to the themes root directory, the new CSS will be:

          body {
          cursor: url('cursor.cur'), auto;
          }
          
          a:hover{
          cursor: url('cursor.cur'), auto!important;
          }
